WEBVTT

00:00:12.533 --> 00:00:20.749 line:90% position:50% align:center
Brother, when I meet you,
I’ll be nice in what I say.

00:00:20.749 --> 00:00:29.300 line:90% position:50% align:center
Brother, I will treat you
With love and kindness ev’ry day.

00:00:29.300 --> 00:00:37.224 line:90% position:50% align:center
I will show you right from wrong.
And when we don’t seem to get along,

00:00:37.224 --> 00:00:44.315 line:90% position:50% align:center
I’ll try to be the big sister
You can trust.

00:00:44.315 --> 00:00:52.156 line:90% position:50% align:center
Our house will be your home.
You have a fam’ly of your own.

00:00:52.156 --> 00:00:59.413 line:90% position:50% align:center
And most of all, Jehovah God—
He will teach you.

00:00:59.413 --> 00:01:03.834 line:90% position:50% align:center
We can’t wait to meet you.

00:01:05.419 --> 00:01:13.594 line:90% position:50% align:center
Brother, just like I did,
You’ll learn from Dad how you can pray.

00:01:13.594 --> 00:01:22.019 line:90% position:50% align:center
Brother, I’m excited
About the games that we will play.

00:01:22.019 --> 00:01:30.069 line:90% position:50% align:center
It won’t be easy to learn to share,
But when you get sad, I’ll show I care

00:01:30.069 --> 00:01:37.159 line:90% position:50% align:center
By try’n’ to be the big sister
You can trust.

00:01:37.159 --> 00:01:44.875 line:90% position:50% align:center
Our house will be your home.
You have a fam’ly of your own.

00:01:44.875 --> 00:01:51.924 line:90% position:50% align:center
And when you come along,
Everyone’ll be there to greet you.

00:01:51.924 --> 00:01:56.929 line:90% position:50% align:center
We can’t wait to meet you.

